@startuml
!pragma layout smetana

title Add Bullet Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant Resumake
participant Parser
participant AddBulletCommand
participant RecordList
participant Record
participant Ui
participant Storage

User -> Resumake: addbullet INDEX / BULLET
Resumake -> Parser: parse(input, ui)
Parser --> Resumake: AddBulletCommand
Resumake -> AddBulletCommand: execute(list)
AddBulletCommand -> RecordList: getRecord(index)
AddBulletCommand -> Record: addBullet(text)
AddBulletCommand -> Ui: show success
Resumake -> Storage: saveToFile(list)
Storage -> Storage: serialize + compare + write if changed
@enduml
